{"tid":1875540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢爛賭大媽無視禁令聚賭被拘 公安擸鎚扑爛麻將枱","createTime":"2020-02-12T00:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T17:39:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":180,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"b090dafe59d9472af5c23dd94bc2a1ddc97b8bb9","tid":1875540,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:06:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在支那大爆發，當局為遏止疫情，不惜實施封城，更禁止公眾場地經營，要求民眾減少聚集。惟支那人「嗜賭大過天」，無視當局禁令，繼續把握機會打牌聚賭，最終被拘捕後，更要當街向公眾認錯。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200211/large/1581419433_3bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581419433_3bf1.jpg&h=a3ba1290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n網上更有流出一段公安發現民眾打牌的影片。公安當場狠斥在場人士，繼而用鐵鎚砸毀電動麻將枱：「現在是國難當頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你們還是這樣&hellip;&hellip;現在疫情這麼嚴重，你們為人父母，為人爺爺奶奶&hellip;&hellip;還在害人，害社會&hellip;&hellip;你們就是為老不尊。」在場人人鴉雀無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200212/2SI753UQBFZDIHPC5DAQZHSUOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200212%2F2SI753UQBFZDIHPC5DAQZHSUOU%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=ea9fe10c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200212%2F2SI753UQBFZDIHPC5DAQZHSUOU%2F&h=1dacfba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200212/2SI753UQBFZDIHPC5DAQZHSUOU/</a>"},{"pid":"9cb11e8ebcfbf7ca44b57b9db9ca65b87b2e6d78","tid":1875540,"uid":1886,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:07:31.000Z","msg":"上周六（8日），江蘇鹽城當局透露，早前拘捕15名聚賭民眾，各人被罰站在街頭公開認錯，對着街坊說：「我們錯了，疫情這麼嚴重，我們還一起打牌，我們保證下不為例！請大家引以為戒，少出門，少聚集，戴口罩，多洗手。」將這個反面教材對外作宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n此外，常州市朝陽橋公安亦發現當地一村落有棋牌室繼續在營業，當時有11人在場，有人甚至未有戴上口罩。公安作出批評教育，在場人員均認錯，甚至表示將報名義工活動，為疫情防控出一分力。當地公安遂安排各人到關口做義工3日。<br />\n<br />\n當日傍晚，湖北仙桃市公安局發現有村民聚集「鬥地主」。警方對涉案者作批評教育，並給予行政處罰。涉案者事後自願協助村內巡查，在卡口當值。<br />\n10日，四川達州市公安局表示，公安於9日有8名民眾在一居民樓地下室打麻將，事後將各人帶返派出所進行教育。涉案者為警惕親友，不惜將自行聚賭的事上傳至微信朋友圈中。"},{"pid":"c5a7b67b144fb7a880e00f2773ede3840fda5cd3","tid":1875540,"uid":102700,"like":156,"dislike":1,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:08:00.000Z","msg":"香港應該扑爛左個人而唔係張枱"},{"pid":"c13fc12496100eb8d26ceb986bdf58ca515c48fa","tid":1875540,"uid":137638,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"有呢種人就算中國有民主又有咩用？"},{"pid":"92a87cd6b60454e10bff7160cdf29e828bca6ac5","tid":1875540,"uid":236854,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:14:16.000Z","msg":"香港班狗會直接扑爆你個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e29df34d93710d8380e8064b742733eedf718e","tid":1875540,"uid":51594,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"中国人是要管的"},{"pid":"dff99acdb97f4a92006e413b8ba484ed1397e60e","tid":1875540,"uid":32699,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:22:33.000Z","msg":"公安作出批評教育，在場人員均認錯，甚至表示將報名義工活動，為疫情防控出一分力。當地公安遂安排各人到關口做義工3日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd2a1e42e90857bc5a77af3711472f1133faa2a","tid":1875540,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:25:37.000Z","msg":"打撚斷對手啦"},{"pid":"f6b035fd30460ae516572a353032b03fa78ca1a5","tid":1875540,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff99acdb97f4a92006e413b8ba484ed1397e60e","tid":1875540,"uid":32699,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:22:33.000Z","msg":"公安作出批評教育，在場人員均認錯，甚至表示將報名義工活動，為疫情防控出一分力。當地公安遂安排各人到關口做義工3日。